metadata:
  generateName: add-song-to-playlist-
spec:
  entrypoint: add-song-to-playlist
  templates:
  - name: add-song-to-playlist
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-playlist-id
        template: get-playlist-id
      - name: add-song
        template: add-song
        dependencies: [get-playlist-id]

  - name: get-playlist-id
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/Playlistname2ID"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "playlist_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.playlist_name }}"
        }
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: playlist_name
        value: "Classic Disco Hits"
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: playlist_ID
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.playlist_ID"

  - name: add-song
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/AddSongToPlaylist"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "user_ID": {{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }},
          "playlist_ID": {{ tasks.get-playlist-id.outputs.parameters.playlist_ID }},
          "song_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.song_name }}"
        }
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: user_ID
        value: "{{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}"
      - name: song_name
        value: "Hey Jude"
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: playlist_songs
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.playlist_songs"
